OL,7,FVideo showing the drugs seized in
OL,8,FSpain's largest synthetic drug bust
OL,10,FSpanish authorities have carried out
OL,11,Ftheir largest-ever confiscation of
OL,12,Fsynthetic drugs after seizing pink
OL,13,Fcocaine and over one million ecstasy
OL,14,Fpills.
OL,16,FAn estimated value of over 25 million
OL,17,Feuros (#21.1 million) worth of drugs
OL,18,Fwas seized across Ibiza and Malaga in
OL,19,FSpain's crackdown, known as Operation
OL,20,FAdriatico.
