OL,7,FAuthorities confiscated 212kg of
OL,8,Fketamine, 73kg of MDMA, 20kg of
OL,9,Fcocaine, 21kg of pink cocaine, 10kg of
OL,10,Fhashish, 6kg of marijuana, 3kg of a
OL,11,Fsubstance used to produce pink
OL,12,Fcocaine, and 1,071,327 ecstasy pills
OL,13,Fweighing 357kg.
OL,15,FThe Guardia Civil, Spain's law
OL,16,Fenforcement agency, said they targeted
OL,17,Fmultiple synthetic drug trafficking
OL,18,Forganisation and arrested nine people.
