OL,7,FOfficers uncovered one specific
OL,8,Fnetwork in Ibiza that sold drugs
OL,9,Fhidden in compartments of cars,
OL,10,Fprompting the investigation.
OL,12,FThis led authorities to intercept a
OL,13,Fcar from the Netherlands at the
OL,14,FSpanish-French border, carrying 25kg
OL,15,Fof synthetic drugs.
OL,17,FThe group had also expanded to Malaga,
OL,18,Fwhere they planned to set up
OL,19,Foperations and broaden their business.
