OL,7,FThe network's key figures were mainly
OL,8,FItalian nationals based in Ibiza, with
OL,9,Fsupport from Spanish and Dutch
OL,10,Faccomplices.
OL,12,FIbiza is one of the most popular party
OL,13,Fdestinations for Brits, with roughly
OL,14,Fone million of us visiting over the
OL,15,F2023 summer season.
OL,17,FExperts from the Balearic party island
OL,18,Fpreviously told ITV News that one
OL,19,Fmajor concern with pink cocaine (also
OL,20,Fknown as tusi) is that it actually
OL,21,Frarely contains any cocaine.
